query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(q tq s) */ select count(*)
from tag_question AS tq
inner join question AS q
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 0 AND q.score <= 5
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('physics')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('conservation-laws',
'energy',
'experimental-physics',
'fluid-dynamics',
'forces',
'homework-and-exercises',
'metric-tensor',
'newtonian-gravity',
'operators',
'quantum-mechanics',
'schroedinger-equation',
'spacetime',
'special-relativity',
'visible-light');
